cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

This paper is about transfer learning for vision tasks using pre-trained representations. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses scaling up pre-training and fine-tuning, which falls under the category of large-scale learning, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. The paper also discusses the use of heuristics for transferring pre-trained representations, which falls under the category of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the performance of the model on various datasets, which falls under the category of Natural Language Processing (cs.CL) and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE).
